&quot;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:宋体;font-size:21.33333396911621px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img src=&quot;http://bcs.duapp.com/creatunion/%2Fimage%2F2014-01-15%2F1389795047-1000.jpg?sign=MBO:E56d21e82c6ead3d4eaa9e2192b93d1d:QoiDV8Li%2Fyxly9j6G1ZgjoYueSM%3D&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:宋体;font-size:21.33333396911621px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	炖柴鸡来喽~\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:宋体;font-size:21.33333396911621px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	忽略这个不大美观的盆。。。。&lt;img src=&quot;http://bcs.duapp.com/creatunion/%2Fimage%2F2014-01-15%2F1389795071-1000.jpg?sign=MBO:E56d21e82c6ead3d4eaa9e2192b93d1d:XSkoGJA1qlVjZ5Bu1fR212PpjAQ%3D&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:宋体;font-size:21.33333396911621px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:宋体;font-size:21.33333396911621px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:宋体;font-size:21.33333396911621px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	味道那是相当的棒 啊！小编瞬间有了一种大厨的赶脚~哈哈。。。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:宋体;font-size:21.33333396911621px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:宋体;font-size:21.33333396911621px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:#FFFF00;&quot;&gt;想来体验农村生活，&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:#00B0F0;color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;垒土锅做饭&lt;/span&gt;，&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:#FF0000;color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;还原农耕生活&lt;/span&gt;的亲们一定&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:#00B050;color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;不能错过亲农耕&lt;/span&gt;哦！！！&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;','','1389795076','1389795076',78,'ljtvtp1389711310','还原真实农村生活——土锅做饭烧炕'),(11,2,'qingnonggeng','亲农耕 简介 1','2','',8,'农场靓照','http://bcs.duapp.com/creatunion/%2F2014-01-16%2F1389870077-1000.jpg?sign=MBO:E56d21e82c6ead3d4eaa9e2192b93d1d:zSyw4Ke%2FU7XS9u%2FhM5o5MfERWWM%3D','1','&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;北农&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;亲农耕农业体验园创建于&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;2008&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;年，位于北京市昌平区马池口镇亭自庄村西，南接百葛路，西靠温南路，距北京市北六环西端&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;公里，占地面积约&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;1023&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;亩。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;亲农耕农业体验园采用多种生态农业模式进行布局，让普通百姓亲自参与到农业的生产生活中来，让人们亲身感受到&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;“&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;农耕&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;的快乐，为都市人群提供参与有机农业，绿色农业的体验场所，让孩子们感受到和农业&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;“&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;接触&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;的快乐。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;亲农耕目前的体验项目有：园区采摘：园区种植体验，现代牧场参观体验，苗圃种植示范，农业知识科普，健康养生休闲，高科技农业示范科普等项目。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;旅游观光紧紧围绕农业生产，利用田园景观、田园文化，在体现自然生态美的基础上，运用美学和园艺核心技术，供游客进行观光、游览、品尝、购物、参与农作、休闲、度假等多项活动。园区依托北京农学院优秀的农业人才，以有机栽培模式采用洁净生产方式生产有机农产品，为人们提供健康、绿色的有机食品。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &lt;span style=&quot;color:#E53333;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;color:#E53333;&quot;&gt;亲农耕：打造高端农业体验园。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;带上你的家人和朋友，让我们一起亲近农业，了解大自然。&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://bcs.duapp.com/creatunion/%2Fimage%2F2014-01-16%2F1389870211-1000.jpg?sign=MBO:E56d21e82c6ead3d4eaa9e2192b93d1d:e0Y65xF0iEd%2BqSIXhWiXLcDWbbw%3D&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;','http://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/appmsg/show?__biz=MjM5NzA3OTkzMg==&amp;appmsgid=10000160&amp;itemidx=2&amp;sign=66ca7e4644be16933cad5c9e39dadf32#wechat_redirect','1389870258','1389870258',85,'ljtvtp1389711310','亲农耕农场简介'),(14,17,'lishiguang','产品 活动 年货','2','各种产品',25,'产品商城','http://bcs.duapp.com/creatunion/%2F2014-01-20%2F1390153775-1000.jpg?sign=MBO:E56d21e82c6ead3d4eaa9e2192b93d1d:cBK8O2x2aN7x8p8VGT55cZje4pQ%3D','1','&lt;img src=&quot;http://bcs.duapp.com/creatunion/%2Fimage%2F2014-01-20%2F1390153762-1000.jpg?sign=MBO:E56d21e82c6ead3d4eaa9e2192b93d1d:JB2QSR8HzYX%2Fv%2Bg2hoQN89X2XH0%3D&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;','','1390153783','1390153818',1,'tdvcwj1390148307','产品介绍'),(15,2,'qingnonggeng','6 八宝诗 农耕八宝诗 亲农耕八宝诗','1','',8,'农场靓照','http://bcs.duapp.com/creatunion/%2F2014-01-21%2F1390305447-1000.jpg?sign=MBO:E56d21e82c6ead3d4eaa9e2192b93d1d:3Mm0EvBXRm2a4DIKHRWcbw9tkOI%3D','0','&lt;img src=&quot;http://bcs.duapp.com/creatunion/%2Fimage%2F2014-01-21%2F1390305467-1000.jpg?sign=MBO:E56d21e82c6ead3d4eaa9e2192b93d1d:rSmCqqDlOPaj59awwow3j9KvAsw%3D&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;','','1390305476','1390305927',18,'ljtvtp1389711310','农耕八宝诗'),(16,2,'qingnonggeng','2 优势 亲农耕优势','1','',8,'农场靓照','http://bcs.duapp.com/creatunion/%2F2014-01-21%2F1390307481-1000.jpg?sign=MBO:E56d21e82c6ead3d4eaa9e2192b93d1d:u%2BIgp4bHx2rfXyvATWVfhPZc5VA%3D','1','&lt;p class=&quot;p0&quot; style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:宋体;font-size:21.33333396911621px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;园区依托北京农学院雄厚的农业技术实力，建设成为北京市农业技术推广示范基地、都市型现代化农业示范展示中心、北京设施农业主题公园，青少年实践基地。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;p0&quot; style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:宋体;font-size:21.33333396911621px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;color:#0000FF;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;设施、资源：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;亲农耕农业体验园里有生态餐厅；垂钓池；休闲四合院；园区餐厅；蘑菇、有机蔬菜、时令蔬菜种植棚数栋；现代化牧场、鸡场、鹿舍；同时园区提供住宿、娱乐等配套服务，让您在辛勤劳作后，品尝特菜，放松休息，享受美好闲暇时光。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;p0&quot; style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:宋体;font-size:21.33333396911621px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;color:#0000FF;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;地理位置：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;距离市区很近的郊区，东临G6（八达岭）高速，G7高速，南靠北六环，据北六环百葛出口仅5公里，行车非常方便。&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;p0&quot; style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:宋体;font-size:21.33333396911621px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://bcs.duapp.com/creatunion/%2Fimage%2F2014-01-21%2F1390307453-1000.jpg?sign=MBO:E56d21e82c6ead3d4eaa9e2192b93d1d:rIxRrZvfLgCBgbLTAP5Kw4bhCR4%3D&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;','','1390307491','1390307491',17,'ljtvtp1389711310','亲农耕优势'),(17,2,'qingnonggeng','5 特色 特色农产品','1','',8,'农场靓照','http://bcs.duapp.com/creatunion/%2F2014-01-21%2F1390307599-1000.png?sign=MBO:E56d21e82c6ead3d4eaa9e2192b93d1d:u7wZzhyjxAixjp%2FsIY0Ap2J45bY%3D','1','&lt;img src=&quot;http://bcs.duapp.com/creatunion/%2Fimage%2F2014-01-21%2F1390307572-1000.png?sign=MBO:E56d21e82c6ead3d4eaa9e2192b93d1d:B%2B